sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Envoy as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy Proxy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant GWCtrl as Gateway Controller

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: User Access to RHOAI Dashboard (Gateway API path)
    User->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Envoy: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS terminate
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443, mTLS (Istio)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: OAuth2/OIDC<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth token
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: Auth result + headers
    Envoy->>Dashboard: HTTPRoute forward<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer token
    Dashboard-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Admin,CompCtrl: Flow 2: Component Deployment Lifecycle
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DataScienceCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create component CRs<br/>(Dashboard, KServe, etc.)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>CompCtrl: Watch notification
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>from /opt/manifests/<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over Admin,GWCtrl: Flow 3: Gateway Infrastructure Setup
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create GatewayConfig CR
    K8sAPI-->>GWCtrl: Watch notification
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create GatewayClass + Gateway<br/>in openshift-ingress
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy kube-auth-proxy<br/>Deployment + Service + HPA
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter +<br/>DestinationRule (Istio)
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth client<br/>(integrated OAuth mode)
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>for /oauth2 path
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create dashboard redirect<br/>resources (nginx + Routes)
